=head1 DESCRIPTION

Configuration information about the S3 bucket where Identity Resolution
Jobs writes result files.

You need to give Customer Profiles service principal write permission
to your S3 bucket. Otherwise, you'll get an exception in the API
response. For an example policy, see Amazon Connect Customer Profiles
cross-service confused deputy prevention
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/connect/latest/adminguide/cross-service-confused-deputy-prevention.html#customer-profiles-cross-service).

